---
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content'; import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'; import ProjectCard from '../components/ProjectCard.astro'; import ArticleCard from '../components/ArticleCard.astro';
const projects = (await getCollection('projects')).filter(p=>p.data.featured);
const articles = (await getCollection('articles')).sort((a,b)=>b.data.pubDate.valueOf()-a.data.pubDate.valueOf()).slice(0,3);
---
<BaseLayout title="张智博" description="关注人工智能、产品创新与项目实践。"><section class="hero"><p class="eyebrow">PERSONAL ARCHIVE / 2026</p><h1>张智博</h1><p class="hero-copy">关注人工智能、产品创新与项目实践。<br/>记录想法如何被理解、被构建，<br/>并最终成为真实的项目与成果。</p><div class="hero-links"><a href="/projects/">查看项目 <i>↓</i></a><a href="/articles/">阅读文章 <i>↓</i></a></div></section><section class="section"><div class="section-heading"><div><p class="eyebrow">SELECTED WORK</p><h2>项目</h2></div><p>一些已经完成、正在推进，或仍在持续思考的项目。</p></div><div class="project-grid project-grid--home">{projects.map((p,i)=><ProjectCard project={p} featured={i===0}/>)}</div><a class="text-link" href="/projects/">查看全部项目 <i>→</i></a></section><section class="section articles-preview"><div class="section-heading"><div><p class="eyebrow">WRITING</p><h2>最新文章</h2></div><a class="text-link" href="/articles/">全部文章 <i>→</i></a></div><div class="article-list">{articles.map(a=><ArticleCard article={a}/>)}</div></section><section class="section evidence"><p class="eyebrow">SELECTED RECORDS</p><h2>成果不是数字墙，<br/>而是项目推进中留下的记录。</h2><div class="evidence-grid"><a href="/achievements/#robotics"><strong>99.2%</strong><span>中邮分拣机器人抓取成功率</span></a><a href="/achievements/#commerce"><strong>300 万元</strong><span>多平台电商双十一单日 GMV</span></a><a href="/achievements/#ip"><strong>11 项</strong><span>国家专利成果</span></a></div></section><section class="section about-teaser"><p class="eyebrow">ABOUT</p><h2>不急着定义身份，<br/>先把正在完成的事留下来。</h2><p>比起给自己一个固定的身份，我更愿意通过持续完成的项目、留下的内容和形成的成果，让这些经历逐渐说明我是谁。</p><a class="text-link" href="/about/">了解更多 <i>→</i></a></section></BaseLayout>
